 UGHELLI – THE Sariki of Arewa community in Uvwie local government area of Delta State, Suleiman Jauro, has disclosed that Fulani herdsmen from Chad, Mali and Niger known as Boros are the brains behind kidnappings and other related crimes by herdsmen in parts of the state. Continue reading Herdsmen from Chad, Mali, Niger behind kidnap of Delta lawyer, 5 others – Arewa community at Vanguard News. Source: Vanguard